PrecisOrder providing for (a) the leasing to the TOWN OF HAY RIVER, for a term of forty-nine (49) years, of some 6,411 square metres of land situate at HAY RIVER AIRPORT which are to be used as the site for a water filtration facility and a waste oil heating plant, and (b) the granting of a licence authorizing them to enter upon the airport grounds in order to operate and maintain an underground water supply line.
